quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  21,58,"Ibraahiima munci sanamuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin haa …ói wonti kuntoy tosokoy, o acci mawndu majji jorto nde …ďe yiltitotoo e mayru fii yo …ďe lanndo ndu ko hommbo munci …ói."
  21,59,"Tuma nde …ďe ruttinoo …ďe tawi sanamuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin muncaama, yoga e ma…ď…ďe lanndii yoga: "Ko hommbo munci rewetee…ói me'en …óin? Pellet, on muncu…óo …ói ko e too√Īoo…ďe …ďen o jeyaa, nokku ka o hoyni …óon ko haani mawninnde e la…ď…ďinnde kon"."
  21,60,"Yoga ma…ď…ďe wi'i: "Men naniino suka no wowla…ói ko boni himo aybina …ói himo wi'ee Ibraahiima, no gasa hara ko kanko munci …ói"."
  21,61,"Koohoo…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen wi'i: "Addee Ibraahiima yeeso yim…ďe …ďen …ďe yi'a mo; belajo'o …ďe seedoto himo qirritoo ko o huuwi kon, qirritagol makko ngol laatanoo on hujja e hoore makko"."
  21,62,"∆Āe addi Ibraahiima (yo o his) …ďe lanndii mo: "Enee, Ibraahiima ko an golle …óee golle kaanu…óe e sanamuuji amen …óin?"!"
  21,63,"Ibraahiima maaki -ko o jalnoroowo …ďe, ko o fen√Īin…óo ronkugol sanamuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin yeeso yim…ďe …ďen-: "Mi wa…óaali …óum, ko woni, gollii …óum mawndu sanamuuji …óin, lanndee sanamuuji mo'on …óin si …ói laatike hi…ói wowla"."
  21,64,"∆Āe ruttori e wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin miijitagol e teskagol …ďanngani …ďe wonnde sanamuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ói nafataa …ói lorrataa, ko kam…ďe woni too√Īu…ďe fewndo …ďe rewunoo…ói gaanin Alla."
  21,65,"Refti …ďe ruttii e sanndal…óaaku e geddi, …ďe wi'i: "Gom…óii hi…óa yananaa -an Ibraahiima- pellet, …óii sanamuuji …ói wowlataa, ko honno yamirirtaa men yo men lanndo …ói?" ∆Āe faandori …óum hujja ma…ď…ďe on, …óum wonti hujja e hoore ma…ď…ďe."
  21,66,"Ibraahiima maaki -ka mettinanngol …ďe-: "Enee, on reway gaanin Alla sanamuuji …ói nafataa on hay e huunde …ói lorrataa on hay e huunde, kannji ko …ói ronku…ói e riiwgol lorra kan gaayi ko'e majji, maa…óum poo…óugol nafa kan fii majji."
  21,67,"On kaanii, ko rewoton kon kadi ko woori Alla kaanii, …óii sanamuuji …ói nafataa …ói lorrataa kadi, enee, on hakkiltaa …óum, …óalon rewugol …ói?!"
  21,68,"Tuma nde …ďe ronkunoo tiindorde mo dalil …ďe wallitori doole …óen, …ďe wi'i: "Sunniree Ibraahiima yiite ngen; wallee sanamuuji mo'on …ói o fusi o munci …óin si tawii on wonii wa…óay…ďe …óum lepte ha…óooje"."
  21,69,"∆Āe hu…ď…ďini yiite …ďe werlii mo e magge, Men Daali: "ko an yo yiite, wonu …ďuu…ďol e kisiyee e dow Ibraahiima, nge woniri non, o he…ďaali lorra"."
  21,70,"Yim…ďe Ibraahiima (yo o his) …ďen faandanii mo pewje fii sunnugol mo, Men bonni pewje ma…ď…ďe …óen, Men wa…ói …ďe kam…ďe halkaa…ďe foolaa."
  21,71,"Men ndanndi mo Men ndanndi kadi Luutu, Men yaltini …ďe, …ďe yahi ka leydi Saami ndin ndi Men barkiniri e mu'un; Nulugol Annabaa…ďe e mayri, e sabu ko Men saakani kon tageefooji …óin e nder mayri immorde e mo∆ī∆īereeji."
  21,72,"Men Okki mo Ishaaqa fewndo o torinoo Joomi makko yo O arsiku mo …ďi…ó…óo, Men Okki mo Yaaquuba ka …ďeydugol, gooto-kala immorde e Ibraahiima e ge…óaljo makko on Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba Men wa…ói …ďe mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …óoftii…ďe Alla."